encode_bits: puts chars in a file into binary
decode_bits: takes binary input and outputs it in ASCII
tooctal: takes numeric input, outputs in octal
todecimal: takes numeric input, outputs in base10
tohex: takes numeric input, outputs in hexadecimal (uppercase)
tobinary: takes numeric input, outputs in binary

getnum() returns a long int in decimal notation
negatives are handled with the use of a global flag

